## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="babf2-102">Applications utilisent le module de reconnaissance partagé pour accéder à la reconnaissance vocale Windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="babf2-102">Applications use the shared recognizer to access Windows Speech Recognition.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="babf2-103">Utilisez le <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> objet à ajouter à l’expérience utilisateur de reconnaissance vocale Windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="babf2-103">Use the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> object to add to the Windows speech user experience.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="babf2-104">Cette classe permet de contrôler des différents aspects du processus de reconnaissance vocale :</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="babf2-104">This class provides control over various aspects of the speech recognition process:</span></span>  
  
